    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @davidpike7, I just did some more fixes on the toggle widget, can you this build on your website: https://gist.githubusercontent.com/vvo/19d16de5d738ab55eaa3a9e1e3c7b67b/raw/71ff01360b6591186142b1457d5add5f40f746a3/instantsearch.min.js\n\nHere's what's new:\n\n``` text\n    feat(toggle): Provide a better default widget\n\n    This update brings:\n    - default to showing the next user action items count instead of the\n    current number of displayed hits\n\n    which means:\n    if checkbox is not checked, show: [ ] free shipping (countWhenChecked)\n    if checkbox is checked, show: [x] free shipping (countWhenNotChecked)\n    - fix numeric based on and off values (fixes #1096)\n    - provide `onFacetValue` and `offFacetValue` template data, fixes #919\n```\n",
